			<p>Before Alex was Alex, he worked in financial sales and trading as well as tech consulting. He is a graduate of Wilfrid Laurier University. When not at the office, Alex plays and coaches Hockey and if you ask politely, he’ll recite the entire poem The Raven by Edgar Allan Poe (Seriously!). Alex joined Rayku to drive traffic, build strategic relationships, and provide service to Rayku’s community of tutors and students. </p>
