			<p>Donny started Rayku to address his previous struggles with homework, having tried alternative solutions with no success. Before Rayku, Donny was the founder of Kinkarso Tech. With entrepreneurship as his life, Donny has spoken at M.I.T. on the subject, was named a 'Top 10 Under 20' by Vancouver Magazine, and is the global recipient of the 2010 Student Entrepreneur of the Year award. When he's not hammering away at the office, Donny enjoys rooting for the Vancouver Canucks, and playing Plants vs. Zombies.</p>
